title: FOODPOLIS Designated Foreign Investment Zone (KDI - Korea Development Institute)
text: ( Source : KDI - Korea Development Institute ) The National Food Cluster of South Korea (FOODPOLIS) has been designated as a foreign investment zone, which lays the stepping stone for the cluster to better become an international food specific
